description:
Back up/Restore your data. DataBackup is based on speed-backup. It was born with the consent of the author. DataBackup is intended to back up and restore the data of your apps. Root access is needed. It works on arm64-v8a(4 as suffix), armeabi-v7a(3 as suffix), x86_64(2 as suffix) and x86(1 as suffix) devices with Android 9 or higher.
Features include: * Multi-user Support * 100% Data Integrity * Fast * Easy * ...
